aa(lp145
VNow in the deluge of information, this is where
p146
aVthe real-time web gets really interesting for a journalist like myself,
p147
aVbecause we have more tools than ever
p148
aVto do that kind of investigation.
p149
aVAnd when you start digging into the sources, you can go
p150
aVfurther and further than you ever could before.
p151
aa(lp152
VSometimes you come across a piece of content that
p153
aVis so compelling, you want to use it, you're dying to use it,
p154
aVbut you're not 100 percent sure if you can because
p155
aVyou don't know if the source is credible.
p156
aVYou don't know if it's a scrape. You don't know if it's a re-upload.
p157
aVAnd you have to do that investigative work.
